text: Lange sticcan feðerecgede, and writ on ægðerne sticcan.
Ælcere ecge an pater noster oð ende.
And lege <þone> an þam berene on þa flore, and þone oðerne on ofer þam oðrum sticcan þæt þær si rode tacn on.
And nim of ðam gehalgedan hlafe þe man halgie on hlafmæssedæg feower snæda & gecryme on þa feower <hyrna> þæs berenes.
